       _n_r_o_f_f formats documents written in the _r_o_f_f(7) language for typewriter-
       like devices such as terminal emulators.

       GNU  _n_r_o_f_f  emulates the traditional Unix _n_r_o_f_f command using _g_r_o_f_f(1).
