       needs to know the character encoding scheme used by the terminal.  Con-
       sequently, acceptable arguments to the --TT  option  are  aasscciiii,  llaattiinn11,
       uuttff88,   and   ccpp11004477;   any   others   are  ignored.   If  neither  the
