       (which  overrides the environment variable) specifies a (valid) device,
       _n_r_o_f_f consults the locale to select an appropriate output  device.   It
       first  tries  the _l_o_c_a_l_e(1) program, then checks several locale-related
       environment variables; see "ENVIRONMENT", below.  If all of the forego-
       ing fail, --TTaasscciiii is implied.

